{"tid":937471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★蘋果iPhone中國禁售？媒體稱走訪發現銷售正常","createTime":"2018-12-11T14:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T04:24:27.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3c7281c78108b630b0c33908c99f8c29ea5dc1d4","tid":937471,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"現據新京報報導，記者走訪位於北京王府井和大望路的兩家專賣店，發現除因停產而停售的iPhoneX等機型外，其他iPhone依然在售。另外，截至發稿，蘋果官網、天貓和京東旗艦店依然能夠選購包括iPhone X在內的多款禁售機型。<br />\n<br />\n此前據摩根士丹利分析師Katy Huberty稱，&ldquo;此禁令看起來範圍有限，因為它僅適用於使用iOS11操作系統的手機。目前蘋果70%的設備都運行iOS12，更重要的是目前在售的所有設備都安裝iOS12。&rdquo;招商電子方競也表示，iPhone銷售暫不受影響，蘋果可通過更新iOS避免侵權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/399/735.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2F0%2F399%2F735.htm&d=Lw1NKwDC7SlkBqgBVo8gC3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=4c951d6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/0/399/735.htm</a>"},{"pid":"64a23070fdf2af88fabea224d274e6b3a6cfdf6d","tid":937471,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T14:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35742662b7217c16c63db255798d66c439f3dc5e","tid":937471,"uid":27202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T14:39:26.000Z","msg":"中国又赢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d747177b03b08520a40a044169a85987af9b01b","tid":937471,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T14:41:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/d57/631/d57631f406306ba3cea5831708febd9cf8e9af3b_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2Fd57%2F631%2Fd57631f406306ba3cea5831708febd9cf8e9af3b_b.jpg&h=a261a664&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b617abd47058ae3216198591f4f